Package com.github.dscpsyl.jgrade2.gradedtest

Class GradedTestResult

java.lang.Object
com.github.dscpsyl.jgrade2.gradedtest.GradedTestResult
public class GradedTestResult extends Object
A class for the data that models a graded test. Primarily based on the data needed for Gradescope's Autograder JSON. When creating GradedTestResults and working with visibility, use the public constants VISIBLE, HIDDEN, etc.
